97681.name: Europe urban population share (Bairoch (1988))
97681.description: The percentage of the population classified as urban. A criterion of 5000 inhabitants is used for urban population.

source.name: Bairoch (1988)
source.dataPublishedBy: Bairoch, P., 1988. Cities and Economic Development, translated by Christopher Braider.
source.additionalInfo: See Table 8.2 (pp. 137), Table 13.5 (pp. 225), Table 26.1 (pp. 414), Table 26.3 (pp. 423), and Table 27.4 (pp. 438) for original data.
